<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">In the field of pharmacy, preparation of documents in the field of profession, with examples, technical translation studies from Turkish to English, and the patterns used in communication are displayed in an interactive manner. Scientific writing rules and methods are explained.</Data></Cell>
