<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">26.08.2025</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">It includes the types of written and oral expression, the process of scientific research, and the issues of showing resources, which should be considered in oral presentations.</Data></Cell>
