<Row>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Faculty of Pharmacy (English)</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">17</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">ACU 149</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Medical Photography</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">1</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">2+0+0</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">2</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">3</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">22.08.2025</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">A passionate journey in which machines can tell the story of a man&apos;s battle for life, triggered by a different creativity that combines the art of photography, medicine and human anatomy: medical photography
Medical photography is a very virgin field in Turkey. Visual content, photography production is a phenomenon that stands out in every sector in today&apos;s world.
The training of Physicians and/or auxiliary medical personnel with basic and medical photography knowledge in this field makes professionals stand out.
First of all, the follow-up of cases, the source of treatment processes to presentations and scientific publications, the creation of impressive uses with visual richness due to quality visual production is the work of medical photography.
It also increases the use in surgical branches by making photo shoots in the operating room environment without affecting surgery.
Of course, it is very important to know the production and use of photographs in accordance with the legislation on legal limitations and rights of use, because all of the productions made by ignoring these issues cannot go beyond wasting labor and time or impose great legal obligations on the doctor and institution.</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=429755&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">OK</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell>
</Row>
