<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Participants of this course will develop a discerning comprehension of the interconnections among ecological, economic, and social systems. They will explore the correlation between urgent environmental challenges and prevalent patterns of production and consumption, while also acquiring knowledge of diverse social sciences methodologies and concepts to scrutinize this phenomenon.</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=429821&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
