<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">22.08.2025</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Dersin İçeriği Translational cancer research is a critical field that focuses on bridging the gap between basic research discoveries and their practical application in clinical settings. The aim of the course you described is to equip BSc (Bachelor of Science) students with a comprehensive understanding of the tools and techniques used in translational cancer research. Here&apos;s a breakdown of what this could entail:
Translational cancer research is a critical field that focuses on bridging the gap between basic research discoveries and their practical application in clinical settings. The aim of the course you described is to equip BSc (Bachelor of Science) students with a comprehensive understanding of the tools and techniques used in translational cancer research. Here&apos;s a breakdown of what this could entail:</Data></Cell>
