<Row>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Faculty of Pharmacy (English)</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">17</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">PHAR 201</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Physiopathology</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">3</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">3+0+0</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">3</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">3</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">04.09.2025</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Definition of pathology, cellular basis of the disease, disease-causing factors, diseases related to malnutrition, morphology, cell injury, inflammation (etiology and inflammation) formation and types (acute, chronic and subacute inflammation), tumors (properties and naming of benign and malignant tumors) etiology and spread, body fluids and blood flow disorders (embolism, ischemia, infarction, hypertension, dehydration, bleeding, shock), metabolism disorders (protein, lipid and carbohydrate metabolism disorders)</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=429770&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">OK</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell>
</Row>
<Row>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Faculty of Pharmacy (English)</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">17</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">PHAR 203</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Biochemistry</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">3</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">3+0+0</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">3</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">3</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">04.09.2025</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">The subject and history of biochemistry, classification of carbohydrates (monosaccharides, dissaccharides and polysaccharides) classification of lipids, stereoid, amino acid definition, general structure, properties, protein structure and properties, classification of proteins and examples, nucleic acid structure and properties, DNA, RNA, enzyme structure and its properties, factors affecting enzymes, enzyme activity control, allosteric enzymes and their properties, vitamins and minerals, water metabolism, bioenergetic and oxidative phosphorylation, digestion and absorption of carbohydrates, glycolysis, glycogenesis, glycogenogenesis, creel cycle, lipids digestion and transport, lipoproteins, lipoprotein metabolism, activation of fatty acids, beta oxidation of saturated and unsaturated fatty acids, synthesis of fatty acids, nucleic acid metabolism, protein metabolism, protein metabolism, hormones and signal transmission mechanisms</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=429667&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">OK</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell>
</Row>
<Row>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Faculty of Pharmacy (English)</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">17</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">PHAR 205</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Physical Pharmacy</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">3</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">3+0+0</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">3</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">3</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">16.10.2025</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">States of matter, phase solubility and colligative properties, solutions, pH-pKa concept, dissolution rate, solution preparation methods, isotonic solutions, inter-surface properties, adsorpsion, rheology and diagrams</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=429721&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">OK</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell>
</Row>
<Row>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Faculty of Pharmacy (English)</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">17</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">PHAR 207</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Analytical Chemistry II</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">3</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">3+0+0</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">3</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">4</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">21.10.2025</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Instrumental analysis techniques including spectroscopic, chromatographic and electrochemical methods</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=429722&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">OK</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell>
</Row>
<Row>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Faculty of Pharmacy (English)</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">17</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">PHAR 209</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Analytical Chemistry II Lab.</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">3</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">0+3+0</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">1,5</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">2</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">21.10.2025</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Introduction to basic instrumental analysis devices used in the laboratory; applications of UV spectroscopy, FTIR, polarimetry, refractometry, thin layer chromatography, column chromatography, HPLC, potentiostat method; obtaining calibration curves; evaluation of the obtained experimental results.</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=429793&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">OK</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell>
</Row>
<Row>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Faculty of Pharmacy (English)</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">17</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">PHAR 223</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Pharmaceutical Microbiology and Immunology</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">3</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">3+0+0</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">3</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">4</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">15.10.2025</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">History of microbiology, definitions of microbiology and pharmaceutical microbiology, classification of microorganisms, criteria used in classification and general features of microbial groups, bacterial cell structure, DNA replication, protein synthesis, sporulation, variations, mutations, mutagenic agents, genetic material transfer in bacteria, exotoxins and endotoxins, vectors, zoonoses, mechanisms of action of chemotherapeutic agents and disinfectants, sterilization and disinfection, interactions between microorganisms, their environment, and host organisms, host resistance to infections, introduction to immunology, immunity, allergy and allergic reactions, autoimmune diseases, transplantation and cancer immunology, vaccines and sera, the role and impact of microorganisms in the pharmaceutical industry, microbiological quality control of pharmaceutical products.</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=429772&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">OK</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell>
</Row>
<Row>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Faculty of Pharmacy (English)</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">17</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">PHAR 233</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Organic Chemistry II</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">3</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">4+0+0</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">4</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">6</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">18.09.2025</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Alcohols and phenols; ethers and epoxides; thiols and sulfides; carbonyl compounds; carboxylic acids and nitriles; Benzene chemistry: electrophilic aromatic substitution; carboxylic acid derivatives; amines</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=429669&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">OK</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell>
</Row>
<Row>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Faculty of Pharmacy (English)</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">17</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">PHAR 250</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Simulated Pharmacy</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">3</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">2+0+0</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">2</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">2</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">14.10.2025</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Developing skills in welcoming patients, reading prescriptions, evaluating, communicating with patients and other stakeholders, analyzing drug brief information, profitability analysis and controls</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=429863&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">OK</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell>
</Row>
<Row>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Faculty of Pharmacy (English)</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">17</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">PHAR 204</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Pharmaceutical Microbiology</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">4</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">2+0+0</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">2</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">3</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">15.10.2025</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">General structure, replication, cultivation, and classification of viruses, DNA viruses, RNA viruses, Gram-positive cocci, Gram-negative cocci, Gram-positive bacilli, Gram-negative bacilli, Gram-negative coccobacilli, Mycobacteria, Nocardia, Actinomycetes, Spirochetes, Rickettsiae, Chlamydiae, Parasitology, Mycology</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=429668&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">OK</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell>
</Row>
<Row>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Faculty of Pharmacy (English)</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">17</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">PHAR 206</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Pharmaceutical Microbiology Laboratory</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">4</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">0+3+0</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">1,5</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">3</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">16.10.2025</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">This course covers the instruments used in the microbiology laboratory, the use of microscopes, and the principles and applications of sterilization and disinfection. The course also covers culture media used in microbiology, bacterial growth, bacterial motility testing, staining techniques, bacterial identification methods, serological reactions, blood group determination, and microscopic examination of blood cells. Additionally, students will learn about antimicrobial susceptibility testing (antibiogram, MIC, E-test), the characteristics of Mycobacteriaceae, parasitological and mycological examinations, as well as microbiological quality control tests of pharmaceutical preparations, including sterility testing, microbial limit testing, and bacterial endotoxin testing.</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=429670&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">OK</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell>
</Row>
<Row>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Faculty of Pharmacy (English)</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">17</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">PHAR 212</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Pharmaceutical Botany</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">4</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">3+0+0</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">3</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">3</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">20.10.2025</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">General concepts related to pharmaceutical botany, scientific terms in botany, taxonomy, classification systems, nomenclature, plant morphology, bacteria, algae, fungi, ferns, seed plants (gymnosperms and angiosperms) will be covered, and the pharmacological activities of medicinal plants will be discussed.</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=429794&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">OK</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell>
</Row>
<Row>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Faculty of Pharmacy (English)</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">17</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">PHAR 214</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Pharmaceutical Botany Lab.</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">4</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">0+4+0</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">2</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">3</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">20.10.2025</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Lichens, fungi, conifers, ferns, roots, bark, stem types, metamorphosis, leaves, fruits, flowers, and finally family identification using a dichotomous key and herbarium preparation will be discussed.</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=429723&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">OK</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell>
</Row>
<Row>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Faculty of Pharmacy (English)</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">17</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">PHAR 216</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Pharmaceutical Chemistry I</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">4</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">3+0+0</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">3</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">3</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">17.10.2025</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Factors affecting drug activity, functional groups, chemical reactions, naming rules, introduction to drug metabolism, laboratory information about synthesis and purification, information on the drug groups described in the course flow.</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=429857&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">OK</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell>
</Row>
<Row>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Faculty of Pharmacy (English)</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">17</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">PHAR 218</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Pharmaceutical Chemistry Lab.I</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">4</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">0+4+0</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">2</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">3</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">20.10.2025</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Laboratory information on synthesis and purification.</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=429747&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">OK</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell>
</Row>
<Row>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Faculty of Pharmacy (English)</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">17</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">PHAR 221</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Public Health</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">4</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">2+0+0</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">2</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">2</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">26.08.2025</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Introduction to public health, epidemiology, environmental health, nutrition, maternal and child health, family planning and prevention methods, communicable diseases, sexually transmitted diseases, health legislation, health management and chronic diseases</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=429785&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">OK</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell>
</Row>
<Row>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Faculty of Pharmacy (English)</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">17</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">PHAR 226</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Pharmaceutical Technology I</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">4</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">3+0+0</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">3</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">3</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">13.10.2025</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Introduction to pharmaceutical technology, basic terminology, pharmacopoeias, prescription-dose calculations, pharmaceutical water types, properties and production, unit pharmaceutical processes (such as grinding, drying, liquid mixing, filtration), types of pharmaceutical solutions, auxiliary substances and excipients in solutions and quality control issues will be examined.</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=429889&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">OK</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell>
</Row>
<Row>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Faculty of Pharmacy (English)</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">17</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">PHAR 228</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Pharmaceutical Technology Lab.I</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">4</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">0+4+0</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">2</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">3</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">16.10.2025</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Introduction to pharmaceutical technology, basic terminology, pharmacopoeias, prescription-dose calculations, pharmaceutical water types, properties and production, unit pharmaceutical processes (such as grinding, drying, liquid mixing, filtration), types of pharmaceutical solutions, auxiliary substances and excipients in solutions and quality control issues will be examined.</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=429762&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">OK</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell>
</Row>
<Row>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Faculty of Pharmacy (English)</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">17</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">PHAR 260</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Pharmacology I</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">4</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">3+0+0</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">3</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">4</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">14.10.2025</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Introduction to pharmacology, passage of drugs through biological membranes, routes of drug administration, absorption, distribution, metabolism and elimination of drugs, drug mechanisms of action, pharmacodynamics, drug-receptor theory, introducttion to autonomic nervous system, cholinergic agents, anticholinergic agents, adrenergic agonists, adrenergic antagonists, central nervous system. effective muscle relaxants, antidepressants, general and local anesthetic drugs, antipsychotic drugs, sedative-hypnotic drugs, antiepileptic drugs</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=429724&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">OK</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell>
</Row>
<Row>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Faculty of Pharmacy (English)</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">17</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">PHAR 295</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Practical Pharmacy Training (Summer Internship)</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">5</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">0+8+0</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">4</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">3</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">12.11.2025</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">To enable intern students to observe the professional knowledge practices and roles of pharmacists in community pharmacies, and to help them gain the necessary experience before entering professional life.</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=429786&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">OK</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell>
</Row>
<Row>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Faculty of Pharmacy (English)</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">17</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">PHAR 301</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Pharmacognosy I</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">5</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">3+0+0</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">3</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">4</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">20.10.2025</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">In the lectures, students are provided with information on the chemical structures, biological effects, and pharmaceutical uses of natural-source medicinal raw materials, primarily herbal drugs.</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=429671&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">OK</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell>
</Row>
