<Row>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Faculty of Pharmacy (English)</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">17</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">PHAR 309</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Pharmaceutical Technology II</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">5</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">3+0+0</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">3</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">3</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">16.10.2025</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Formulation of pharmaceutical forms such as bi-phase systems (liquid-solid, liquid-liquid and liquid-gas), ointments, gels, suppositories, injection dosage forms, radiopharmaceuticals, production methods and quality control, applications for the investigation and prevention of incompatibility. Biopharmaceutical, pharmacokinetics, bioavailability and bioequivalence concepts and formulation parameters that affect bioradiation. Bioavailability determination and evaluation. The importance of bioequivalence, in vitro and in vivo equivalence assays, evaluation issues will be covered.</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=429796&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">OK</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell>
</Row>
