<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">5</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">3+0+0</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">3</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">4</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">14.10.2025</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Autacoids; Histamine and antihistamine drugs, peptide structured autocoids, serotonin agonists and antagonists. arachidonic acid metabolites and prostanoids, anti-inflammatory drugs, drugs used in the treatment of rheumatoid arthritis and gout, antihypertensive and diuretic drugs, antianginal and antiarrhythmic drugs, vasodilators, hypolipidemics, other drugs used in the treatment of heart failure, hypolipidemic and antithrombotic drugs, expectorants, mucolytics and antitussive drugs, bronchodilator and other antiasthmatic drugs and drugs used in the treatment of chronic obstructive pulmonary disease.</Data></Cell>
