<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">General definition of quantitative analysis
Titrimetric analysis methods
Quantitative analysis using titrimetric analysis
Understanding the HPLC system
Using known samples in HPLC
Using unknown samples in HPLC
NMR spectroscopic methods
IR, NMR, and MS spectral data analysis</Data></Cell>
