<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Covers topics such as powders, tablets, manufacture of tablets, capsules, manufacture of capsules, control of solid dosage forms, aerosols, radiopharmaceutics, controlled delivery systems, microspheres, microcapsules, drug delivery system such as liposomes, properties, manufacture, quality control, packaging and dosage forms used in veterinary medicine.</Data></Cell>
