<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Intellectual and industrial property rights, protection of inventions by patent and utility model documents, patent-criterion of useful model, patent and parts of patenting, patent application paths, legislation, benefits of patent protection, non-patentable subjects, right to claim and extortion, workers&apos; inventions, university members&apos; discoveries, basic principles of patent / utility model certificate, types of patents, legal processes in patent applications, costs, objections, decree law, license status, patent and utility model documents invalidity and infringement, patent and utility model certificate the scope and interpretation of the invention, the selection of experts and expert opinions, preparation of the expert report, data protection and data concession, patent agreements, criminal cases, patent research, evaluation of patent violations with various examples rs content.</Data></Cell>
