<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">2+0+0</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">2</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">3</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">20.10.2025</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">The basic characteristics of the medical materials used in human health directly and indirectly, the identification and classification of the basic properties and the effective and safe use of these materials will be taught. Medical equipment, equipment used in oxygen therapy, hypodermic equipment, thermometers, surgical yarns, ostomy materials, corsets, urine bags, urinals, catheters, cotton, gauze, surgical materials and the information about the use and regulation of these materials will be given.</Data></Cell>
