<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">General definitions related to phytotherapy; regulations and legislation concerning the subject worldwide and in Turkey; information on bioavailability, pharmacokinetics, and pharmacodynamics of herbal drugs; risks associated with herbal drugs; plants beneficial for the protection and treatment of human health, based on the results of scientific research, are classified according to the organs they affect; the active components and modes of action of important plants.</Data></Cell>
