<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">23.10.2025</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Toxicology, toxic response, dose and limits, toxicity mechanisms, risk concept, mutagenicity and carcinogenicity, as well as daily exposure to non-pharmaceutical substances such as food additives and heavy metals from a toxicological perspective</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=429684&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
