<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Introduction to pharmacokinetics. speed processes, zero and first order kinetics, single compartment and multi compartment systems, adaptation of rate processes to pharmacokinetics, half-life, rate constants and virtual distribution volume concepts, bioavailability and bioequivalence, clearance concept, renal and hepatic clearance, intravenous infusion, multiple dose regimens and dose calculations.</Data></Cell>
