</Row>
<Row>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Faculty of Pharmacy (English)</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">17</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">ACU 150</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Historical Continuity from the Ottoman to the Republic</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">1</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Gain information about the Ottoman Empire that ruled before the Republic of Turkey, comprehend the transition process from Ottoman to Republic. learn the social and cultural heritage that was transferred from the Ottoman Empire to the Republic, evaluate the historical continuity phenomena from the Ottoman Empire to the Republic, establish a connection between the past and the present and be able to make comment on the topics.</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=429760&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
</Row>
<Row>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Faculty of Pharmacy (English)</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">17</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">ACU 151</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Digital Photography and Photo Processing Techniques</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">1</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Define photography, master the process of photography from film to digital, and establish its historical context, understand how the camera works and how it records.</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=429749&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
</Row>
<Row>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Faculty of Pharmacy (English)</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">17</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">ACU 151</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Digital Photography and Photo Processing Techniques</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">2</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Explain the concept of accurate exposure within the framework of photosensitive surface, photosensitivity, light measurement and light qualities, explain alternative correct exposures in terms of clear depth of field and recording movement.</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=429749&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
</Row>
<Row>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Faculty of Pharmacy (English)</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">17</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">ACU 151</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Digital Photography and Photo Processing Techniques</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">3</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Explain the technological possibilities offered in the camera, the process of photographic film and printing, and digital photography technology, define general image editing rules</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=429749&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
</Row>
<Row>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Faculty of Pharmacy (English)</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">17</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">ACU 151</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Digital Photography and Photo Processing Techniques</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">4</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Gain information about how to use a camera</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=429749&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
</Row>
<Row>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Faculty of Pharmacy (English)</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">17</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">ACU 151</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Digital Photography and Photo Processing Techniques</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">5</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Recognize photo processing programs, explain the basic features of Photoshop software, define the process of visual preparation before printing. Describe the relationship between the tools and menus of the software in image preparation, apply program usage information at basic level, discuss the results of basic image preparation studies. and design a visual image for printing and the web.</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=429749&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
</Row>
<Row>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Faculty of Pharmacy (English)</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">17</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">ACU 152</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Professional Presentation Design</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">1</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Define the basic elements needed to make a presentation.</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=429748&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
</Row>
<Row>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Faculty of Pharmacy (English)</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">17</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">ACU 152</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Professional Presentation Design</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">2</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Interpret the possibilities of the tools used in the presentation event.</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=429748&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
</Row>
<Row>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Faculty of Pharmacy (English)</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">17</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">ACU 152</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Professional Presentation Design</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">3</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Recognize and use the tools such as PowerPoint, Keynote, Photoshop, Premiere Pro, and Illustrator.</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=429748&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
</Row>
<Row>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Faculty of Pharmacy (English)</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">17</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">ACU 152</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Professional Presentation Design</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">4</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Express themselves creatively and innovatively.</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=429748&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
</Row>
<Row>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Faculty of Pharmacy (English)</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">17</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">ACU 152</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Professional Presentation Design</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">5</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Define and implement all stages of the presentation. Make presentations using effective presentation and persuasion techniques.</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=429748&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
</Row>
<Row>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Faculty of Pharmacy (English)</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">17</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">ACU 153</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">How to Read a Photo?</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">1</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Have the necessary equipment to read the photos they see. In this way, they will understand the photos that exist in both the media and our daily (private) lives, change the way they interpret them, understand how visual language is used in visual culture, and gain the ability to interpret them.</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=429759&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
</Row>
<Row>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Faculty of Pharmacy (English)</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">17</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">ACU 154</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Cultural Memory: How We Remember, Why We Forget</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">1</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Students who successfully complete the course will recognize ‘cultural memory &apos; as a concept and content. In addition, they will be able to understand and analyze how and in what forms cultural memory feeds our existence, identity in relation to concepts such as remembering, forgetting, nostalgia, popular culture, individually and culturally in our daily lives</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=429758&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
</Row>
<Row>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Faculty of Pharmacy (English)</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">17</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">ACU 155</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Time and Stress Management</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">1</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Question their perspective on time and the concept of activity</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=429673&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
</Row>
<Row>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Faculty of Pharmacy (English)</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">17</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">ACU 155</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Time and Stress Management</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">2</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Identify their goals and key areas that will lead them to their goals</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=429673&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
</Row>
