<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">3</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">They can learn about pesticide toxicity and take the necessary precautions in daily life. Can give information about intoxication of natural toxicants and treatment approaches.</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=429897&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
